'''Phindian''' language was the native language of the [[Phindian/Legends|Phindian]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Phindar/Legends|Phindar]]. Phindian was formed basically of soft sibilants and vowel sounds, which were significantly longer than those of other languages. Most Phindians were fluent in both Phindian and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

